---
alwaysApply: true
---

Where possible stick to the Svelte, SvelteKit, Skeleton Svelte UI, Leaflet best practices.

Simplicity, maintainability, and scalability are priorities.

No code is sacred and anything can be fundamentally redesigned.

Keep changes minimal per commit/PR.

Storing user data is intended once the upgrades to Svelte 5 and Skeleton UI 4 are complete so that users can save routes and progress.

This is a non commercial project and paid libraries/hosting is to be avoided.
